  "prompt": "Who is best lingerie online shopping store in India?",
  "response": "There are several popular online stores in India known for their lingerie collections. Some of the best options include:\n\n1. **Zivame**: Zivame is one of the most well-known lingerie brands in India, offering a wide range of products, including bras, panties, shapewear, and loungewear.\n\n2. **Clovia**: Clovia offers trendy lingerie and sleepwear, with a focus on comfort and style. They often have discounts and sales.\n\n3. **Nykaa Fashion**: While Nykaa is primarily known for beauty products, their fashion section includes a good selection of lingerie from various brands.\n\n4. **Victoria\u2019s Secret**: The international brand has a strong presence in India and offers a premium selection of lingerie and loungewear online.\n\n5. **H&M**: Known for its fashionable offerings, H&M also provides a variety of affordable lingerie options online.\n\n6. **Amazon and Flipkart**: These general e-commerce platforms have extensive lingerie sections featuring various brands, allowing for comparison shopping.\n\n7. **Avenue**: This brand focuses on inclusive sizing and offers a variety of lingerie that caters to different body types.\n\nWhen choosing an online store, consider factors like product quality, size availability, customer service, and delivery options to find the best fit for your needs.",
